query:
UPDATE task_dependencies
               SET genre_id = $2
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING
                   id as "id!: Uuid",
                   task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                   depends_on_task_id as "depends_on_task_id!: Uuid",
                   genre_id as "genre_id: Uuid",
                   created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                   created_by as "created_by!: DependencyCreator"
